  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n- This is about the time we publish attestations compared to 1/3 of slot (so -2 means 1s after slot, +2 means 6s after slot\r\n- On goerli it rarely happens\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1291\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-12-07 at 16 00 48\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/206134702-0473c9ff-f98d-40cd-b245-53271d4e8e45.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n- However some mainnet nodes (v1.2.x) experienced this issue more\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1285\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-12-07 at 16 00 27\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/206134616-a0d5e9b3-a7fc-4de4-a356-c020d00341b6.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nAttestations should be published not later than 1/3 of slots",
